Hello!! Posting for the one and only, the impalpable, and unstoppable Dragon Lady of Biringan. 🐉 ✨

For context, she has successfully secured locker 2F-105. However, mukhang may ibang nagkamali po ng lagay ng gamit at nilagyan po ng lock. 

Kindly coordinate with Schelleymar Cruz (2022077332) via Teams or Outlook. Thank you so much.

Cc: Schelleymar Galvez
       Microsoft
       Netflix

𝗝𝗢𝗜𝗡 𝗧𝗛𝗘 𝗦𝗨𝗣𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧! 🛡️

The backbone of every mission is a strong support team—and this is your call to action! Here are the guidelines for non-performing member applications.

🗓️ 𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗣𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗼𝗱: September 10–16, 2025 (FORM CLOSES AT 11:59 PM)

📌 Step up, bring your strategy, and help assemble a winning team. May your application hit the mark! 🎯

Pubmat By:
Hisami Muramatsu
Ian Canlas
Micaella Alegiojo

Caption By: Mae Saeed

#TamHunt2025 
#MembershipApplications2025
#AfterGround
#ITHMGroovers
